9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 656, L.D. 1648, “Resolve, to Honor
10 Margaret Chase Smith and Joshua Chamberlain in the National Statuary Hall”
11 Amend the resolve by striking out the title and substituting the following:
12 'Resolve, to Honor Margaret Chase Smith and Joshua Chamberlain in the National
13 Statuary Hall Collection'
14 Amend the resolve in section 1 in the last line (page 1, line 14 in L.D.) by inserting
15 after the following: "House." the following: 'The commissions shall accept private gifts,
16 grants and donations from individuals and organizations to fund the costs of replacing the
17 statues of Hannibal Hamlin and William King in the National Statuary Hall Collection with
18 the statues of Margaret Chase Smith and Joshua Chamberlain and to transport and display
19 those statues within public view within the State House or, if feasible, on the grounds of
20 the State House.'
21 Amend the resolve by inserting after section 1 the following:
22 'Sec. 2. Appropriations and allocations. Resolved: That the following
23 appropriations and allocations are made.
24 MUSEUM, MAINE STATE
